      <section>
        <h3>What information Boxy SVG collects and why</h3>

        <section>
          <h4>Information from App visitors</h4>

          <p>Like most web app operators, Boxy SVG collects basic non-personally-identifying information from
          App visitors of the sort that web browsers and servers typically make available, such as the browser
          type, language preference, referring site, and the date and time of each visitor request. We collect
