          visitors, and to monitor security of the App.</p>

          <p>Boxy SVG also collects potentially personally-identifying information like IP addresses from
          visitors. Boxy SVG does not use such information to identify or track individual visitors, however.
          We collect this information to understand how visitors use the App, to improve performance and
          content, and to monitor security of the App.</p>

          <p>Boxy SVG may collect statistics about the behavior of visitors to our App. For instance, Boxy SVG
          may reveal how many views a particular file got using aggregated statistics that contain anonymous
          user information only.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h4>Personally-identifying information</h4>

          <p>Users of the App may choose to interact with Boxy SVG in ways that provide us with their
          personally-identifying information. The amount and type of information that Boxy SVG gathers depends
          on the nature of your interaction with us, as well as the amount of information you choose to share.
          For example, we ask visitors who want to publish content on the App to provide a username and email
          address to identify them.</p>

